🌍  The Browser Battle: Google Chrome vs. Microsoft Edge vs. Mozilla Firefox

Situation: Your friend complains their computer is slow, and you see 50 Chrome tabs open.
Debate: Which browser offers the best mix of speed, privacy, and efficiency?

🔴 Team Chrome: “Feature-rich and tightly integrated with Google tools.”

🔵 Team Edge: “Fast, secure, and power-efficient.”

🟠 Team Firefox: “Privacy-first, open-source, and lightweight.”
